            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-heart-empty" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <h1 class="cover-heading">Go Climate Neutral!</h1>
            <p class="lead">By each month investing in the certified climate offset projects that has the most positive impact for the environment for you - with a sum that corresponds to your lifestyle - we can help you offset your climate footprint. This way you can live an as climate neutural life as possible over time.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="site-wrapper-inner site-wrapper-second">
        <div class="cover-container">
          <div class="inner cover">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-up" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <h1 class="cover-heading">It's fun to do it together!</h1>
            <p class="lead">By offseting your climate impact with us, you inspire others to do the same. Climate change is a challange we face together, so we should fight it together as well. And it's fun seeing the impact we can make together and follow the process over time.</p>
