          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-search" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <h1 class="cover-heading">We are 100% transparent</h1>
            <p class="lead">We are 100% transparent in which climate offset projects we invest in, and why. We are also 100% transparent with the amount corbon we manage to offset with your help, and how much carbon we manage to offset with the help of all of our users.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </div>

