            <p class="lead">97.5% of what you offset for goes directly to the most effective climate reducing projects we can find. The other 2.5% goes to covering our costs and for marketing to get even more people to live a more climate neutral life. This is excluding any credit card fees that may apply depending on which country you live in.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </div>

